Wednesday, October 4, 2000

MERIT DOCKET

00-660. USX Corp. v. Penn Cent. Corp.

Cuyahoga App. No. 74755. On motion to strike motion to dismiss. Motion denied.

On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
